n of a powerful little alien that you may or may not have stolen/liberated from the evil Empire. As the Empire closes in, you'll need to find a way to balance your ship's management with the onslaught of attacks. Do you have what it takes to survive?"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Icon.png", "id": "1324311035174797", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38984472_1324311038508130_2610060411856834928_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Iht3D8fMiTYQ7kNvgHSMwVo&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB_HRE04TPqjsSRI-5ImWvuIJJn5YxZAevtZlDtifg8nw&oe=670A53F8"}, {"file_name": "CoverImage_Portrait.png", "id": "1021944422558335", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031612_1021944425891668_3460677483354056217_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=pdRr6gr5mQYQ7kNvgGEYI5z&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCgh6eByduWNVnRu_Yr-DCQFBboRKV6hoXECNImT5-5Bg&oe=670A53FE"}, {"file_name": "CoverImage_Square.png", "id": "998366967853309", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031369_998366971186642_4701792016341896524_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=vRYqfVTe3FgQ7kNvgFcAa7G&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB5DmeD7yQlkZ5rw870DqBUJz8Fu4ljqwL7B13aJ3Aoqw&oe=670A6143"}, {"file_name": "Logo.png", "id": "973425620588096", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/86610716_973425627254762_5218087471640407679_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=5P12Qf3ROTEQ7kNvgEa5M2C&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB8VbhL8KLavfZd2G3vkBEfmkOHqckf70GF2n_qYkbi4w&oe=670A7A81"}, {"file_name": "CoverImage_Landscape.png", "id": "822780949101586", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75557065_822780952434919_8573226718553